title: Kyle Stersic - The Grey Blue Rind - [mp3 320]
description:
The Grey Blue Rind is the third album produced by Kyle Stersic. It is a mixture of low and high fidelity versions of the same songs compiled over the years. The music has jazz, rock, avant-garde and classical influences.


Kyle Stersic - Alto/Tenor Sax, EWI (electronic wind instrument), Piano/Rhodes/Organ, Acoustic/Slide/Electric Guitar, Bass, Percussion, Tape/Drum Loops, Tape Effects/Self Sampling, Circuit Bent stuff,  Percussion, Drums, Vocals
